OL,3,CRyanair fails to compensate family
OL,4,Cafter damaging adapted buggy
OL,6,FA family says they feel "angry" and
OL,7,F"dismissed" by Ryanair after the
OL,8,Fairline refused to compensate them for
OL,9,Fdamage caused to a specially adapted
OL,10,Fbuggy used by their adopted son, who
OL,11,Fhas Cerebral Palsy.
OL,13,FLisa, from Pencoed, and her family
OL,14,Fflew from Cardiff Airport to Malaga
OL,15,Fwith Ryanair in July 2025. But when
OL,16,Fthey landed, they discovered the
OL,17,Fbrakes on their adapted buggy were no
OL,18,Flonger working.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
