FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776863483
OL,3,CRyanair fails to compensate family
OL,4,Cafter damaging adapted buggy
OL,6,F"We flew out with a perfectly good,
OL,7,Fworking piece of equipment that gives
OL,8,Fmy son respite with his Cerebral
OL,9,FPalsy," Lisa told ITV Wales' Consumer
OL,10,FAffairs Correspondent, Kate Lewis.
OL,12,FThat wasn't the only damage the family
OL,13,Fsays was caused by the airline.
OL,15,F"When we actually got to the hire car,
OL,16,Fthinking we could collapse our broken
OL,17,Fbuggy, we actually found out we
OL,18,Fcouldn't even do that," Lisa said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776863483
OL,3,CRyanair fails to compensate family
OL,4,Cafter damaging adapted buggy
OL,6,FAs a result, the family said they had
OL,7,Fto hire a bigger vehicle, which meant
OL,8,Fpaying out more money.
OL,10,FThe cost of a new specially adapted
OL,11,Fbuggy ranges from #1,200 to #1,700.
OL,13,FLisa and her partner, Nathan, who have
OL,14,Ffostered seven children and have three
OL,15,Fof their own, reported the issue
OL,16,Fimmediately to Ryanair staff at Malaga
OL,17,Fairport, but were told they needed to
OL,18,Flog the issue online and only had
OL,19,Fseven days to do so.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776863483
OL,3,CRyanair fails to compensate family
OL,4,Cafter damaging adapted buggy
OL,6,F"We put the claim in, and then the
OL,7,Ffirst four days of the holiday were
OL,8,Fspent back and forth with Ryanair
OL,9,Fbecause you can't speak to a human
OL,10,Fbeing. You send them these emails, you
OL,11,Ffollow all the links they ask you to,
OL,12,Fand you have to wait hours for a
OL,13,Fresponse."
OL,15,FBut the impact continues far beyond
OL,16,Fthe holiday. Lisa described the
OL,17,Fsituation as a "total injustice to
OL,18,Fchildren with additional needs,"
OL,19,Fadding: "We've managed since July last
OL,20,Fyear with loans and equipment that
OL,21,Fdoesn't suit his needs."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776863483
OL,3,CRyanair fails to compensate family
OL,4,Cafter damaging adapted buggy
OL,6,FAfter nearly a nine-month fight,
OL,7,FRyanair closed the case without paying
OL,8,Fcompensation because Lisa could not
OL,9,Fprovide proof of purchase.
OL,11,FLisa said she purchased the buggy
OL,12,Fsecond hand on for just under #1000,
OL,13,Fand does not have a proof of purchase
OL,14,Freceipt.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the airline said: "We
OL,17,Fregret that this passenger's buggy was
OL,18,Fdamaged when travelling from Cardiff
OL,19,Fto Malaga on 21 July.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
