PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776863483
OL,3,CRyanair fails to compensate family
OL,4,Cafter damaging adapted buggy
OL,6,F"This passenger submitted a claim on
OL,7,F24 July 2025 and was informed that
OL,8,Fsame day that a member of Ryanair's
OL,9,FCustomer Service team was reviewing
OL,10,Ftheir claim and requested the original
OL,11,Fpurchase receipt and an invoice for
OL,12,Fthe repair or replacement of the buggy.
OL,14,F"However, this passenger has yet to do
OL,15,Fso."
